    "The global pooling process can be denoted as follows:",
    "where NN stands for neural network.",
    "Figure 4a illustrates the overall architecture of global pooling and Table 1 presents representative open-source graph pooling methods.",
    "In Fig. 4a, the global pooling consists of three consecutive graph convolutional layers, where the outputs of each layer are concatenated and fed into the graph pooling layer to perform downsampling operations.",
